Body: Description: We are a partner. When we login with account mauro.vecchiato@sanmarcogroup.it, it asks to reset password. After we insert the password (the one just used to login) we got error "The password provided is different from the existing password." How can we access the online console?

What We've Learned Updated: The customer could not access their EPP Server UI with their credentials.  We performed a password reset procedure to allow the customer to login with the root administrator again with the default password.
Next Steps Updated: Issue resolved in remote session. Case can be closed.
